Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.32,0:00:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0...[T1]Akai[T2]...]
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.32,0:00:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinto muito, Momose.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.95,0:00:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Akai!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.29,0:00:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Akai[T0!]
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.05,0:00:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Akai[T0...]
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.51,0:00:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Akai[T0! Akai[T1]!]
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.10,0:00:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Meu Deus...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.23,0:00:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Akai[T0!]
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.31,0:00:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Vou carregá-lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.19,0:00:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Midorikawa, exponha o núcleo para mim.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.32,0:00:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.65,0:00:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Disparando canhão Heigus.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.40,0:00:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.53,0:00:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Momose?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.24,0:00:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Seu desgraçado!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.74,0:01:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Me devolva meu Akai{**-kun}!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Fique longe, Momose!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.13,0:01:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Braços placentários!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.30,0:01:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Espalhem-se!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.34,0:01:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Momose!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.30,0:01:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Escute-nos, Momose!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.18,0:01:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.35,0:01:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Fique aqui, Midorikawa!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.02,0:01:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.60,0:01:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Momose!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.28,0:01:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Corra... Momose...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.62,0:01:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Estrutura de Midorikawa, danos graves.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.00,0:01:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Momose, parada cardiorrespiratória.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.79,0:01:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,O esquadrão de subjugação foi aniquilado.
