Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.37,0:15:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Consegui!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.62,0:15:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.50,0:15:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze, encontro com Honoka e Hoshijiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.96,0:15:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparar para retornar.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.92,0:15:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunato no comando.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.59,0:15:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu encontrei o Kabizashi.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.01,0:15:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Vou coletá-lo agora.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.35,0:15:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Bom trabalho.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.10,0:15:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Comandante!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.47,0:15:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mudança na trajetória do G487.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.89,0:16:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Está seguindo para o esquadrão de recuperação.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.85,0:16:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.27,0:16:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunato, apresse-se e recupere o Kabizashi!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.86,0:16:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Falando Kunato.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.11,0:16:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Missão concluída.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.53,0:16:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nós voltaremos agora.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.03,0:16:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparem-se para retornar.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.16,0:16:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Formação em quarteto.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.63,0:16:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,O esquadrão de recuperação iniciou o retorno.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.92,0:16:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.88,0:16:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Os Gauna não conseguirão acompanhar\Ncom uma formação em quarteto.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mantenham a calma e retornem.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.72,0:16:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
