Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.60,0:16:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,G487 está fazendo algo novo.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.48,0:16:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A placenta dele parece estar mudando.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.85,0:16:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.39,0:16:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Transmitindo vídeo.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.90,0:16:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.70,0:16:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Esquadrão de recuperação, dissolvam a formação.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.37,0:16:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dissolvam-se imediatamente!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.08,0:17:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Reação de Partícula Heigus do G487!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.71,0:17:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Está mirando na equipe de recuperação!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.38,0:17:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossível!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.29,0:17:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dissolvam a formação imediatamente!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.93,0:17:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.06,0:17:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Os Gauna dispararam um canhão de Partícula Heigus?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.89,0:17:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Mas...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.23,0:17:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,En!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Dano severo em todos os frames!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.36,0:17:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Link perdido para os frames de Kunato e Nand Honoka!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.69,0:17:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Retransmitindo vídeo.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.74,0:17:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Qual o status da tripulação?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.03,0:17:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A tripulação parece ilesa.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.74,0:17:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,O dano no frame é severo, porém, apenas o frame de Nand está operacional.
