Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nem o rádio está funcionando.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Como estão os demais frames?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.72,0:18:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele não se mexe.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.72,0:18:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Talvez eu deva reiniciá-lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.62,0:18:02.68,DefaultAlt,,0,0,0,,Aqui é o Hoshijiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.68,0:18:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Meu motor Heigus está com problemas!{My Hyggs engine is working irregularly!}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.35,0:18:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshijiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.77,0:18:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,O motor Heigus do Hoshijiro está fora de controle.\Nis
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.15,0:18:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Está acelerando rapidamente\Npara longe de Sidonia.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.53,0:18:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshijiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.20,0:18:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Desliguem os propulsores! Rápido!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.32,0:18:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Não consigo! Eu não tenho controle!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.04,0:18:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Você consegue desacoplar seus propulsores?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.29,0:18:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Não! Não há resposta!
