Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Não! Vai explodir!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.63,0:18:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu vou me retirar.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.09,0:18:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Estrutura de Hoshijiro perdida.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.23,0:18:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ataque!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.15,0:18:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Estrutura de Hoshijiro perdida!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.48,0:18:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Contato com o piloto perdido!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.40,0:18:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Os Gaunas estão agora a menos de 2000 km de distância.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.32,0:18:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Você consegue me ouvir, Tanikaze?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.78,0:19:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Recolher Honoka e Kunato e evacuar a área imediatamente.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.53,0:19:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Como ele pode ter um canhão de Heigus...?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.95,0:19:05.16,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,{bg}Você consegue me ouvir, Tanikaze?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.16,0:19:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}E um tão grande...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.95,0:19:10.17,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,Recolher Honoka e Kunato e evacuar a área imediatamente.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.29,0:19:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Aquela luz vermelha pode ser um órgão de distribuição Heigus, e se for...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.17,0:19:11.67,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,{bg}Você consegue me ouvir, Tanikaze?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.67,0:19:15.05,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,{bg}Recolher Honoka e Kunato e evacuar a área imediatamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:17.80,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,Responda! Tanikaze!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.60,0:19:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze pegou o Kabizashi\Ne está se aproximando dos Gauna.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.93,0:19:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,O que ele está planejando?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.69,0:19:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Obedeça suas ordens, Tanikaze!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.94,0:19:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Reúna seus camaradas e evacue!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.31,0:19:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A reação de Hyggs dentro do Gauna.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.07,0:19:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze, você está tentando ser isca?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.15,0:19:41.13,DefaultAlt,,0,0,0,,Ele está se aproximando dos Gauna.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.13,0:19:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sério?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.24,0:19:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,O que você está fazendo, Nagate?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.16,0:19:45.24,DefaultAlt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Responda, Tanikaze!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.58,0:19:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Os Gaunas dispararam seu canhão de partículas Heigus.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.72,0:20:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,O G487 perdeu grande parte da sua placenta!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.43,0:20:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Núcleo exposto!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.97,0:20:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele estava mirando uma explosão de interferência Heigus?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.35,0:20:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sem mudança de curso para o Gauna ou para a estrutura de Tanikaze.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.48,0:20:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Ele realmente...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,T menos 5 segundos até o contato.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.98,0:20:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}4...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.24,0:20:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}3...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}2...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.24,0:20:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}1...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.99,0:20:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Contato.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.42,0:20:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.47,0:20:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Incrível.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.89,0:20:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Desintegração da bolha G487 confirmada.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.55,0:20:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze derrotou os Gaunas.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.77,0:20:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze não está ferido.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.95,0:21:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagate matou os Gauna!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.08,0:21:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Comando para as esquadras de defesa.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.58,0:21:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,O G487 foi derrotado por Tanikaze.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.25,0:21:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Repito.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.08,0:21:16.42,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,Comando para as esquadras de defesa.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.12,0:21:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Aquele cara pilotando o Tsugumori não está nada mal.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.42,0:21:20.59,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,O G487 foi derrotado por Tanikaze.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.59,0:21:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze Nagate, hein?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.05,0:21:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.13,0:21:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Partam para resgatar o esquadrão de recuperação.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.39,0:21:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.55,0:21:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Hum...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.93,0:21:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze, você não está ferido?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.10,0:21:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim, estou.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.48,0:21:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum... Eu vou procurar o Hoshijiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.99,0:21:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Por favor, resgatem Kunato e Honoka.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.11,0:21:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.16,0:21:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze, espere!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.16,0:21:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.41,0:21:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Volte, Tanikaze!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.04,0:21:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Não faça isso, Tanikaze{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.87,0:21:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dano na estrutura de Tanikaze: grave.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.50,0:22:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Armazenamento de partículas Heigus baixo.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.50,0:22:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Por favor, tenha cuidado.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.46,0:22:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze, se você for mais longe,\Nvocê não vai conseguir voltar para a Sidônia!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.80,0:22:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu sei a velocidade de Hoshijiro no momento em que ela fugiu.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.26,0:22:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sem alteração no curso de Tanikaze.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.56,0:22:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele está prestes a cruzar a linha sem retorno.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.39,0:22:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0...[T1]Tanikaze...]
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.06,0:22:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu sei.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.39,0:22:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinto muito.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.81,0:22:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Link cortado.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.77,0:22:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze cruzou a linha sem retorno.
